time to create a society and a world and to dwell on character,

33:12.900 --> 33:27.500
characterization. A short story tends to be one little piece, one particular
scene, one particular incident. particularly with Aventine stories. It's a mood

33:27.500 --> 33:41.780
that's created. It's kind of a night gallery kind of mood, I think, probably. In
