33:41.800 --> 33:53.940
would be very concise. But I think dealing with a little punch, you know, boom,
here's one idea. Yes, look it over and here

33:53.940 --> 34:02.520
it is. Whereas the novel, you deal with a lot of complex ideas and a long span
